Christopher S. Sotos

Age : 45Public asset : 2,786,627 USDLinked companies :  NRG Energy Inc -  NRG Yield Inc -  FuelCell Energy Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Christopher S. Sotos is Senior VP-Strategy, Mergers & Acquisitions at NRG Energy, Inc. and Chief Executive Officer at NRG Yield LLC.He is on the Board of Directors at FuelCell Energy, Inc. and NRG Yield, Inc. Mr. Sotos was previously employed as a Principal by Entergy Wholesale Commodities, Treasurer by NRG Generation Holdings, Inc., and a Principal by Service Corp. International.He received his undergraduate degree from Indiana University.



