Christopher S. Sotos



Mr. Christopher S. Sotos is Independent Director at FuelCell Energy, Inc., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at NRG Yield, Inc., Senior VP-Strategy, Mergers & Acquisitions at NRG Energy, Inc. and Treasurer at NRG Generation Holdings, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at FuelCell Energy, Inc. and NRG Yield, Inc. Mr. Sotos was previously employed as a Principal by Entergy Wholesale Commodities and a Principal by Service Corp. International. He received his undergraduate degree from Indiana University.



